description: Reference libraries for Project Arrhythmia modding
releaseNotes:
# 24.11.2 [alpha]
*bug fixes / UI tweaks / new healing system*

## Features
- Added in alt + [ / ] for changing layers on an object.
- Test of new healing mechanic on checkpoint get. (subject to change and feedback)

## Changes
- Better checkpoint animations.
- Better keyboard shortcuts menu.
- Minor improvements to UX / UI in editor.
- Add early access warning.

## Fixes
- Fix for going down to jump to another menu in saves menu.
- More fixes to selection escaping save menu.
- Fix for marker UI.
- Can no longer save in arcade.
- Fix for autosave being generated for arcade mode.

## Known Issues
- There are still some issues with the new dragging editor feature.
- Game UI effects sometimes don't display properly due to jumping between scenes accidently resetting them will fix soon.

### Expect a bigger update probably around this weekend.

# [Alpha] -/- [Default]
This build is an experimental release and thus isn't being considered for default till some refinement. Expect some bugs with the new features.
